<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
        <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pr-24 md:pr-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left mb-16 md:mb-0 items-center text-center">
          <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Building Peace, Empowering Communities
            <br class="hidden lg:inline-block">Across Africa
          </h1>
          <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">At Peace Humanitarian Initiative, we're dedicated to fostering sustainable peace and development through community-driven solutions. Our work transforms lives by addressing the root causes of conflict and poverty, creating lasting change for generations to come.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="/donate" class="inline-flex text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">Donate Now</a>
            <a href="/mission" class="ml-4 inline-flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-200 rounded text-lg">Our Mission</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6">
          <img class="object-contain w-full h-auto max-h-96" alt="Peace Dove - Symbol of Hope and Harmony" src="/public/peace-dove-hero.png" style="background: transparent;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR MISSION</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Building a Peaceful Future Together</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">At Peace Humanitarian Initiative, we are committed to fostering sustainable peace and development through community-driven solutions and collaborative efforts that create lasting positive change.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap">
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Peacebuilding</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Promoting dialogue, reconciliation, and social cohesion through community-based peace initiatives and conflict resolution programs.</p>
            <a href="/mission#peacebuilding" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Humanitarian Aid</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Providing essential support and resources to communities affected by conflict, natural disasters, and humanitarian crises.</p>
            <a href="/mission#humanitarian" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Community Development</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Empowering communities through education, skills training, and sustainable development initiatives that create long-term opportunities.</p>
            <a href="/mission#development" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Advocacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Championing human rights, social justice, and policy changes that support peace and sustainable development goals.</p>
            <a href="/mission#advocacy" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/mission'" class="flex mx-auto mt-16 text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">Our Full Mission</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full mb-20">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full mb-6 lg:mb-0">
            <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-2 text-gray-900">Our Impactful Projects</h1>
            <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-blue-500 rounded"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="lg:w-1/2 w-full leading-relaxed text-gray-500">Discover how PHI is making a difference through our community-driven initiatives. Each project is designed to create sustainable change and empower communities across Africa.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4">
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="/public/projects/peace-education.jpg" alt="Peace Education Program">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">EDUCATION</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Peace Education Initiative</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Empowering youth with conflict resolution skills and peacebuilding education to create future community leaders.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="/public/projects/water-project.jpg" alt="Clean Water Access">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">WATER</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Clean Water Access</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Providing sustainable clean water solutions to communities affected by water scarcity and contamination.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="/public/projects/women-empowerment.jpg" alt="Women's Empowerment">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">EMPOWERMENT</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Women's Leadership</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Supporting women with skills training and resources to become leaders in their communities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="/public/projects/agriculture.jpg" alt="Sustainable Agriculture">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">AGRICULTURE</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Sustainable Farming</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Promoting climate-smart agricultural practices to ensure food security and economic stability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Stay Connected With PHI</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Subscribe to our newsletter for the latest updates on our projects, success stories, and how you can get involved in making a difference.</p>
        </div>
        <form class="flex lg:w-2/3 w-full sm:flex-row flex-col mx-auto px-8 sm:space-x-4 sm:space-y-0 space-y-4 sm:px-0 items-end">
          <div class="relative flex-grow w-full">
            <label for="full-name" class="leading-7 text-sm text-gray-600">Full Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="full-name" name="full-name" required class="w-full bg-white rounded border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 focus:bg-transparent focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-200 text-base outline-none text-gray-700 py-2 px-3 leading-8 transition-colors duration-200 ease-in-out">
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex-grow w-full">
            <label for="email" class="leading-7 text-sm text-gray-600">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full bg-white rounded border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 focus:bg-transparent focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-200 text-base outline-none text-gray-700 py-2 px-3 leading-8 transition-colors duration-200 ease-in-out">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg font-medium">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>